    • Field Detail

      • NEWEST_K_VERSIONS_SELECTED_KEY

        public static final String NEWEST_K_VERSIONS_SELECTED_KEY
        The number of newest versions to select. Only one of NEWEST_K_VERSIONS_SELECTED_KEY and NEWEST_K_VERSIONS_NOTSELECTED_KEY can be specified. The default is NEWEST_K_VERSIONS_SELECTED_KEY with a value of #VERSIONS_SELECTED_DEFAULT_INT. Valid values are in the range [MIN_VERSIONS_ALLOWED, MAX_VERSIONS_ALLOWED].
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • NEWEST_K_VERSIONS_NOTSELECTED_KEY

        public static final String NEWEST_K_VERSIONS_NOTSELECTED_KEY
        The number of newest versions to exclude from the result. Only one of NEWEST_K_VERSIONS_SELECTED_KEY and NEWEST_K_VERSIONS_NOTSELECTED_KEY can be specified. The default is NEWEST_K_VERSIONS_SELECTED_KEY with a value of VERSIONS_SELECTED_DEFAULT. Valid values are in the range [MIN_VERSIONS_ALLOWED, MAX_VERSIONS_ALLOWED].
